OL,4,CCaerphilly gambler cons friends with
OL,5,Cdad funeral lie
OL,6, A gambler conned friends out of #30,000
OL,7, - claiming it was for his father's
OL,8, funeral when he was using it to fund
OL,9, his addiction.
OL,11,FThey felt "betrayed" and "heartbroken"
OL,12,Fwhen they found out he was still alive,
OL,13,FCardiff Crown Court heard.
OL,15,FScott Newland, 25, from Caerphilly,
OL,16,Fdefrauded 11 people over a six-month
OL,17,Fperiod last year, with one friend
OL,18,Fgiving him #10,000.
OL,20,FHe admitted the offences and was
OL,21,Fsentenced to 28 months in prison.
